dct_title_s: Descriptio Boloniae Pontieu; comit. S. Pauli cum adjacentibus.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Decorative title cartouche and ships can compass rose on the ocean. Does not match any atlases listed in van der Krogt. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 45 x 55 cm.
